<C>__{helen}
<D>__{supper's laid out in the kitchen.}
<C>__{mrs. stephens}
<D>__{if you're not back early, you'll find me laid out with it!}
<C>__{helen}
<D>__{we'll be early! good night, darling.}
<C>__{mrs. stephens}
<D>__{good night...}
<A>__{mark holds the door open for helen and she goes into the passage. mark turns and takes a long look at mrs. stephens. she is in the middle of raising her glass. she stops suddenly, the glass poised mid air. he goes out closing the door. she finishes her drink as if it is her last.}
